text.autoconfig.terracraft.title: terracraft Configuration
text.autoconfig.terracraft.option.genera: Everlasting foods cooldown
Cooldown in ticks for the Everlasting
Beef and Eternal Steak items
Play extra hurt sounds
Play animal hurt sounds when taking damage with
the Kitty Slippers or Bunny Hoppers terracraft
Show first person gloves
Whether gloves should display on
the player's hand in first person
Show tooltips
Whether terracraft should have a tooltip explaining their
effect. These can still be found in REI when disabled
Stopwatch MPH
Sets the Stopwatch to use mph instead of km/h
Disable Corruption Spread
Disables the spread of the Corruption Biome
Corruption blocks will no longer spread
Use this for big servers to reduce world lag
Corruption Spread Rarity
How rarely Corruption blocks spread
The higher the value the slower the Corruption spreads
text.autoconfig.terracraft.option.worldg: Accessory rarity
Affects how common terracraft are (does not affect mimics)
When this is 1, the default accessory spawn rates will be used
Values higher that 1 will decrease spawn rates while values lower than 1 will increase spawn rates
Doubling this value will (roughly) halve the chance a container contains an accessory
Setting this to 10000 will completely prevent terracraft from spawning
When set to 0, every container that can contain terracraft will contain an accessory
Enable Corruption
Enables or Disables the Corruption biomes
Cave Chests
Chest rarity
A higher number means less frequent generation
Also depends on the density and shape of caves
Mimic chance
Probability for a mimic to spawn
instead of a loot container
Ore vein chance
Probability for an ore vein to
generate underneath cave chest
Minimum Surface y-level
Minimum y-level to generate surface chests at
Maximum Surface y-level
Maximum y-level to generate surface chests at
Minimum Cave y-level
Minimum y-level to generate cave chests at
Maximum Cave y-level
Maximum y-level to generate cave chests at
Deep Cave y-level
Below this y-level cave chests are considered deep cave
